Title: Culling the Deep
Description:
Have you seen these deepflayers before? Well, of course you have! You were almost eaten by one!

They're getting a little too cozy to me and my people's settlement nearby, and need to be dealt with. Inside the cave, outside the cave, they're all over the place!  That's why I came here in the first place.

Since I can tell we'll be ramblin' round with each other for a bit, why not give me a hand?
